":187595,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-07T18:48:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNot necessarily a rocket.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"GarrisonChisholm","CreatedById":146403,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-07T22:39:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNow do it with Kerbalism.\u00A0\u00A0 \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:cool:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cool.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:cool:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Minmus Derp","CreatedById":187595,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-06-07T23:01:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI personally don\u0027t like kerbalism. Now I\u0027ll just ping, say, \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/188565-fraston/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022188565\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/188565-fraston/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Fraston\u003C/a\u003E for no reason.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}